00:00:00,040 --> 00:00:14,740
( Watch on Kissasia.vip )

1
00:01:00,100 --> 00:01:02,900
=Daughter of Fortune=

2
00:01:02,900 --> 00:01:05,460
(Adapted from the novel
"Phoenix Palace Dream" by Lan Jiujiu)

3
00:01:05,540 --> 00:01:08,490
=Episode 6=

4
00:01:08,490 --> 00:01:11,740
(Tinglan Palace)

5
00:01:16,160 --> 00:01:16,880
Handan,

6
00:01:16,880 --> 00:01:17,880
what took you so long?

7
00:01:18,120 --> 00:01:19,160
Did you get the medicine?

8
00:01:19,440 --> 00:01:20,520
Hurry and apply it for me.

9
00:01:29,920 --> 00:01:30,680
Why are you hiding?

10
00:01:30,700 --> 00:01:32,560
Didn't you want to
learn the art of seduction?

11
00:01:33,360 --> 00:01:34,600
I will teach you right now.

12
00:01:35,560 --> 00:01:37,400
(Why would he
suddenly reveal his identity?)

13
00:01:40,520 --> 00:01:41,280
Attendant Li,

14
00:01:41,400 --> 00:01:42,840
what nonsense are you talking about?

15
00:01:42,880 --> 00:01:44,320
Is this part of the lesson too?

16
00:01:44,520 --> 00:01:45,280
Black Zhen Liquor

17
00:01:45,640 --> 00:01:46,920
can make people tell the truth.

18
00:01:47,880 --> 00:01:49,160
You knew who I was all along,

19
00:01:49,280 --> 00:01:50,520
and yet you're still pretending.

20
00:01:52,880 --> 00:01:54,400
(He has been drugged.)

21
00:01:58,600 --> 00:01:59,960
(What did I say?)

22
00:02:00,120 --> 00:02:01,390
(How much does he actually know?)

23
00:02:01,600 --> 00:02:02,160
Your Majesty,

24
00:02:02,560 --> 00:02:04,320
you should summon
the imperial physician now

25
00:02:04,360 --> 00:02:05,640
to avoid any harm to your health.

26
00:02:08,400 --> 00:02:09,800
Don't you want my favor?

27
00:02:10,840 --> 00:02:11,760
You on top,

28
00:02:12,360 --> 00:02:13,440
and I below.

29
00:02:14,280 --> 00:02:15,400
What's the matter?

30
00:02:16,200 --> 00:02:17,400
Are you afraid now?

31
00:02:17,840 --> 00:02:18,840
Your Majesty is mistaken.

32
00:02:19,600 --> 00:02:21,280
I want the heart of a powerful figure

33
00:02:21,360 --> 00:02:22,120
who is decisive

34
00:02:22,120 --> 00:02:23,000
and stands above all,

35
00:02:23,920 --> 00:02:25,960
not a heart controlled by drugs.

36
00:02:33,200 --> 00:02:34,840
Shen Zhinian,

37
00:02:35,960 --> 00:02:37,200
you...

38
00:02:38,960 --> 00:02:40,200
Very well.

39
00:02:45,320 --> 00:02:47,440
(He didn't get angry
at my deception and refusal.)

40
00:02:47,960 --> 00:02:49,160
(It seems this risky move)

41
00:02:49,440 --> 00:02:50,680
(was the right one.)

42
00:03:01,520 --> 00:03:03,440
(Shen Zhinian,)

43
00:03:04,280 --> 00:03:06,680
(playing hard to get with me, are you?)

44
00:03:07,040 --> 00:03:08,840
(Just you wait.)

45
00:03:12,640 --> 00:03:14,160
Young Lady, please stop playing.

46
00:03:14,400 --> 00:03:15,760
Aren't you afraid?

47
00:03:15,760 --> 00:03:18,320
Why would a snake
suddenly appear on your bed?

48
00:03:18,640 --> 00:03:20,080
Fortunately, you weren't bitten.

49
00:03:20,240 --> 00:03:21,680
This is just too dangerous.

50
00:03:24,360 --> 00:03:25,360
Look at this snake.

51
00:03:25,480 --> 00:03:26,480
It's quite interesting.

52
00:03:27,240 --> 00:03:29,120
As soon as I reach out,
it crawls into my hand.

53
00:03:29,520 --> 00:03:30,440
If I don't let it up,

54
00:03:30,520 --> 00:03:31,840
it even hangs its head

55
00:03:32,120 --> 00:03:33,360
as if it's feeling sad.

56
00:03:33,920 --> 00:03:35,600
The Emperor has arrived!

57
00:03:35,960 --> 00:03:36,720
(Oh no.)

58
00:03:37,040 --> 00:03:38,360
(He's here to settle the score?)

59
00:03:47,680 --> 00:03:48,800
Your Majesty

60
00:03:49,040 --> 00:03:50,480
is here to hold me accountable?

61
00:03:51,520 --> 00:03:52,920
You should know very well

62
00:03:53,240 --> 00:03:54,720
what I'm here for.

63
00:03:55,280 --> 00:03:56,320
I am dull-witted

64
00:03:56,340 --> 00:03:57,720
and do not know your intentions.

65
00:03:57,840 --> 00:04:00,160
If you, who could pretend
not to know me to get close,

66
00:04:00,400 --> 00:04:01,400
are dull-witted,

67
00:04:01,760 --> 00:04:03,640
then there is no
clever person in this palace.

68
00:04:04,320 --> 00:04:06,680
I was indeed looking for Attendant Li.

69
00:04:06,840 --> 00:04:08,840
I just didn't expect
Your Majesty to be there.

70
00:04:09,640 --> 00:04:10,520
I was afraid,

71
00:04:10,520 --> 00:04:11,840
so I could only play along

72
00:04:12,040 --> 00:04:12,880
and continue the act

73
00:04:13,040 --> 00:04:13,800
with Your Majesty.

74
00:04:16,480 --> 00:04:18,080
You actually know how to be afraid, huh?

75
00:04:21,300 --> 00:04:22,400
Your Majesty, you can't read!

76
00:04:22,600 --> 00:04:23,640
This is a book for women.

77
00:04:24,080 --> 00:04:25,180
- How bold.
- Your Majesty.

78
00:04:28,000 --> 00:04:29,520
I insist on taking a look.

79
00:04:35,380 --> 00:04:35,860
(Fishing Alone on the Autumn River)

80
00:04:35,860 --> 00:04:36,380
(Cold waves shimmer
in the autumn light.)

81
00:04:36,380 --> 00:04:36,860
(A lone fisherman
in a straw cloak angles in the sunset.)

82
00:04:36,860 --> 00:04:37,500
(Drunk, lying among reed flowers
with wind-filled sleeves.)

83
00:04:37,500 --> 00:04:38,020
(Waking to the setting moon
and a boat covered in frost.)

84
00:04:39,120 --> 00:04:40,120
Go back.

85
00:04:42,940 --> 00:04:45,740
(Investigation Records
of Nangong Xuanyu)

86
00:04:51,360 --> 00:04:53,320
You've investigated thoroughly,
haven't you?

87
00:04:58,520 --> 00:04:59,400
Why are you hiding?

88
00:05:00,760 --> 00:05:02,120
Now, you're scared?

89
00:05:08,080 --> 00:05:09,280
I entered the palace

90
00:05:09,400 --> 00:05:10,800
solely for Your Majesty.

91
00:05:11,160 --> 00:05:12,400
Investigating you

92
00:05:13,000 --> 00:05:15,040
was also because
I wanted to win your favor.

93
00:05:16,040 --> 00:05:17,040
How did you find out?

94
00:05:17,640 --> 00:05:18,960
When I entered the palace,

95
00:05:18,960 --> 00:05:20,840
my father gave me 300 taels of silver.

96
00:05:21,480 --> 00:05:23,240
To investigate
Your Majesty's preferences,

97
00:05:23,560 --> 00:05:24,720
I have spent them all.

98
00:05:27,200 --> 00:05:28,120
Liar.

99
00:05:34,240 --> 00:05:36,520
So it was you who stole
my little white snake.

100
00:05:36,920 --> 00:05:37,760
Speak.

101
00:05:38,000 --> 00:05:39,120
Who put you up to this?

102
00:05:39,800 --> 00:05:40,920
No one put me up to it.

103
00:05:41,160 --> 00:05:42,280
It came here on its own.

104
00:05:42,880 --> 00:05:44,800
It suddenly appeared
on my bed last night.

105
00:05:45,080 --> 00:05:46,320
I couldn't get it to leave.

106
00:05:46,440 --> 00:05:47,640
I didn't know it was yours.

107
00:05:47,800 --> 00:05:48,680
Shen Zhinian,

108
00:05:49,880 --> 00:05:51,880
if I don't get my
little white snake back,

109
00:05:52,160 --> 00:05:53,520
I will sentence you to death.

110
00:05:56,080 --> 00:05:56,800
Yes, Your Majesty.

111
00:06:05,720 --> 00:06:07,000
Where are you?

112
00:06:07,520 --> 00:06:08,560
Come out quickly.

113
00:06:08,920 --> 00:06:10,360
Your master is here.

114
00:06:10,480 --> 00:06:12,240
Two hours have already passed.

115
00:06:12,600 --> 00:06:13,720
If you still can't find it,

116
00:06:13,920 --> 00:06:16,200
beware that I will sentence you
to death by white silk.

117
00:06:20,040 --> 00:06:20,960
Do you like this?

118
00:06:21,120 --> 00:06:22,000
Come out.

119
00:06:22,200 --> 00:06:23,240
I'll give it to you.

120
00:06:23,640 --> 00:06:24,720
You don't actually think

121
00:06:24,900 --> 00:06:26,080
it will listen to you, do you?

122
00:06:28,360 --> 00:06:29,360
It's coming out.

123
00:06:42,240 --> 00:06:43,520
(Nangong Xuanyu,)

124
00:06:44,200 --> 00:06:46,360
(I'm not only going to
make your snake obey me,)

125
00:06:46,780 --> 00:06:48,400
(but I'm also going
to make you obey me.)

126
00:06:48,800 --> 00:06:50,760
(You really have
many tricks up your sleeve.)

127
00:06:51,680 --> 00:06:53,400
(I have no time to
play with you anymore.)

128
00:06:54,540 --> 00:06:55,120
Your Majesty.

129
00:06:59,680 --> 00:07:01,080
I've been kneeling for so long,

130
00:07:02,480 --> 00:07:03,560
I can't stand up.

131
00:07:04,480 --> 00:07:05,520
Could you

132
00:07:06,160 --> 00:07:07,360
give me a hand?

133
00:07:07,950 --> 00:07:11,820
♪Faint rouge hides
the tenderness in the eyes♪

134
00:07:11,820 --> 00:07:15,380
♪Every step is treacherous,
regardless of the world♪

135
00:07:15,380 --> 00:07:19,050
♪Flowers wither easily,
but obsession remains♪

136
00:07:21,720 --> 00:07:24,080
(They say emperors
have always been heartless.)

137
00:07:24,720 --> 00:07:26,160
(Nangong Xuanyu,)

138
00:07:26,600 --> 00:07:28,240
(you are no exception.)

139
00:07:28,240 --> 00:07:31,780
♪Time silently scars those left behind♪

140
00:07:31,780 --> 00:07:35,570
♪I walk through the palace
day and night, just for my beloved♪

141
00:07:35,570 --> 00:07:38,700
♪All my tenderness is for you,
I'd stay alone for you♪

142
00:07:38,890 --> 00:07:42,300
♪I don't ask for equality,
only that you hear me♪

143
00:07:42,300 --> 00:07:45,490
♪Years of longing haunt
the palace gates, too deep to hide♪

144
00:07:45,490 --> 00:07:49,030
♪I endured the years,
guarding a single truth♪

145
00:07:49,240 --> 00:07:52,500
♪Spending my youth on deep love,
asking not of right or wrong♪

146
00:07:54,360 --> 00:07:56,280
(Met you first under the moonlight,)

147
00:07:56,600 --> 00:07:59,000
(and my heart began to race.)

148
00:07:59,600 --> 00:08:01,200
(I only wish that when the dream ends,)

149
00:08:01,400 --> 00:08:03,000
(you will still be here.)

150
00:08:04,000 --> 00:08:05,520
(Warmth behind the red curtains,)

151
00:08:06,640 --> 00:08:07,920
(entwined with you.)

152
00:08:09,480 --> 00:08:10,760
(Nangong Xuanyu,)

153
00:08:11,720 --> 00:08:12,640
(your heart)

154
00:08:13,200 --> 00:08:14,520
(is racing for me.)

155
00:08:14,600 --> 00:08:15,520
Your Majesty.

156
00:08:16,740 --> 00:08:17,320
Your Majesty.

157
00:08:17,600 --> 00:08:18,360
What is it?

158
00:08:18,400 --> 00:08:19,440
Dowager Consort Liu encountered

159
00:08:19,440 --> 00:08:21,230
bandits on her way
back from Nanhua Temple.

160
00:08:21,240 --> 00:08:23,390
Fortunately, she was saved by
scholars traveling for the exams.

161
00:08:23,400 --> 00:08:24,590
She will return to
the palace tomorrow morning.

162
00:08:24,600 --> 00:08:26,320
Will you go to
the palace gate to receive her?

163
00:08:26,640 --> 00:08:28,360
This dynasty is ruled by filial piety.

164
00:08:28,920 --> 00:08:29,840
If I don't go,

165
00:08:30,400 --> 00:08:32,000
Jiang Chen will nag me about it again.

166
00:08:33,840 --> 00:08:35,160
(He mentioned Jiang Chen.)

167
00:08:36,040 --> 00:08:38,580
(I didn't expect that he and Jiang Chen
were on such good terms.)

168
00:08:39,600 --> 00:08:41,280
Your Majesty is not
looking for the snake?

169
00:08:43,000 --> 00:08:44,160
I don't need to look for it.

170
00:08:45,360 --> 00:08:46,720
It will return on its own.

171
00:08:51,040 --> 00:08:52,480
If it dares to run away again,

172
00:08:53,720 --> 00:08:54,640
I'll stew it.

173
00:08:59,560 --> 00:09:00,880
Your Majesty is formidable.

174
00:09:01,160 --> 00:09:02,440
It wouldn't dare run away again.

175
00:09:02,800 --> 00:09:04,080
Regarding the little white snake,

176
00:09:04,180 --> 00:09:05,440
do not speak of it to anyone.

177
00:09:05,640 --> 00:09:06,400
Yes, Your Majesty.

178
00:09:07,160 --> 00:09:08,200
Shen Zhinian,

179
00:09:08,680 --> 00:09:09,840
tomorrow, follow me

180
00:09:10,210 --> 00:09:11,640
to welcome the Dowager Consort back.

181
00:09:12,310 --> 00:09:13,520
I obey Your Majesty's command.

182
00:09:19,600 --> 00:09:21,160
The white snake is finally back.

183
00:09:21,880 --> 00:09:23,720
This snake was born
on the peak of Mount Tian.

184
00:09:23,920 --> 00:09:25,960
It takes a century
to grow as thick as a thumb.

185
00:09:26,560 --> 00:09:29,360
Without it, when the poison
acts up on the full moon,

186
00:09:29,520 --> 00:09:30,960
Your Majesty could never survive it.

187
00:09:33,660 --> 00:09:35,800
Your Majesty was so intimate
with Shen Zhinian today,

188
00:09:36,000 --> 00:09:37,040
and you're letting her follow you

189
00:09:37,040 --> 00:09:38,700
to welcome Dowager Consort Liu tomorrow.

190
00:09:38,710 --> 00:09:40,080
Does this mean you trust her now?

191
00:09:40,960 --> 00:09:42,240
I just feel

192
00:09:42,560 --> 00:09:44,280
that being near her helps alleviate

193
00:09:44,280 --> 00:09:45,400
this scorching pain.

194
00:09:46,440 --> 00:09:49,080
Besides, no matter whose side she's on
or what her goal is,

195
00:09:50,560 --> 00:09:52,720
in the end,
she'll be just like this snake,

196
00:09:53,240 --> 00:09:55,000
staying obediently
in the palm of my hand.

197
00:09:56,720 --> 00:09:59,320
The Dowager Consort
has returned to the palace!

198
00:09:59,800 --> 00:10:01,280
Mount Nanhua has always been peaceful.

199
00:10:01,960 --> 00:10:03,600
How could you encounter bandits there?

200
00:10:04,160 --> 00:10:05,400
Your Majesty may not know,

201
00:10:05,600 --> 00:10:06,640
but this group of bandits

202
00:10:06,920 --> 00:10:09,040
(Dowager Consort Liu, Empress Dowager of Daliang)
used a four-year-old child to get close to me.

203
00:10:09,200 --> 00:10:11,200
Fortunately, two passing heroes
came to my rescue.

204
00:10:11,560 --> 00:10:13,960
That is how I was able to return safely.

205
00:10:14,320 --> 00:10:15,080
Guards,

206
00:10:15,280 --> 00:10:17,040
please invite the two heroes
into the hall.

207
00:10:26,300 --> 00:10:27,920
(Shen Nanqiao, legitimate
daughter of the Shen family in Chizhou)

208
00:10:27,920 --> 00:10:29,040
(Lu Jianglin, husband of Shen Nanqiao)
Shen Zhinian,

209
00:10:29,320 --> 00:10:30,720
you must seize

210
00:10:31,000 --> 00:10:32,640
this fortune.

211
00:10:32,640 --> 00:10:34,120
The harem

212
00:10:34,120 --> 00:10:35,720
is quite an eventful place.

213
00:10:41,320 --> 00:10:42,280
Execute!

214
00:10:42,920 --> 00:10:43,960
(Shen Nanqiao.)

215
00:10:44,120 --> 00:10:45,400
(Lu Jianglin.)

216
00:10:45,400 --> 00:10:47,000
(How did they get into the palace?)

217
00:10:47,000 --> 00:10:48,940
- Greetings, Your Majesty.
- Greetings, Your Majesty.

218
00:10:49,040 --> 00:10:49,880
You may rise.

219
00:10:50,080 --> 00:10:51,660
- Thank you, Your Majesty.
- Thank you, Your Majesty.

220
00:10:52,120 --> 00:10:53,480
Nanqiao and Jianglin

221
00:10:53,480 --> 00:10:54,840
disregarded their own safety

222
00:10:55,200 --> 00:10:56,440
to save me.

223
00:10:56,440 --> 00:10:57,720
They lured the bandits away

224
00:10:57,720 --> 00:10:59,000
and nearly lost their lives.

225
00:10:59,120 --> 00:11:01,280
Nanqiao even injured
her hand because of it.

226
00:11:01,480 --> 00:11:05,440
So, I brought her back
to the palace for medical treatment.

227
00:11:05,760 --> 00:11:08,560
(It seems Shen Nanqiao knew
the Dowager Consort would be in danger,)

228
00:11:08,840 --> 00:11:10,880
(so she rushed to
the rescue ahead of time)

229
00:11:10,880 --> 00:11:12,240
(to win her favor.)

230
00:11:12,560 --> 00:11:13,880
(When it comes to palace affairs,)

231
00:11:13,880 --> 00:11:15,580
(she is more familiar
with them than I am.)

232
00:11:15,680 --> 00:11:16,960
(If she manages to stay,)

233
00:11:16,960 --> 00:11:18,370
(she will be a huge problem for me.)

234
00:11:19,280 --> 00:11:21,480
Miss Shen, you also share
the surname Shen

235
00:11:22,000 --> 00:11:23,360
and come from Chizhou.

236
00:11:23,840 --> 00:11:25,200
Do you happen to know

237
00:11:25,640 --> 00:11:26,520
Senior Attendant Rou?

238
00:11:35,040 --> 00:11:35,800
Zhinian.

239
00:11:49,700 --> 00:11:54,820
♪Broken dreams,
listening to the light rain♪

240
00:11:56,540 --> 00:12:01,780
♪Bitter cold, bringing mist to the eyes♪

241
00:12:03,420 --> 00:12:05,780
♪If we don't meet♪

242
00:12:05,980 --> 00:12:09,220
♪Flowers bloom and fall in shame♪

243
00:12:09,420 --> 00:12:15,940
♪If we meet again,
the peaches will be warm♪

244
00:12:16,300 --> 00:12:22,740
♪Spring breeze passes,
dancing through the years♪

245
00:12:23,100 --> 00:12:29,420
♪Brewing longing,
remembering past lives♪

246
00:12:29,940 --> 00:12:36,620
♪Hard to meet, and just as hard to part♪

247
00:12:36,620 --> 00:12:43,500
♪Who planted the beans
that grew into lotuses?♪

248
00:12:43,740 --> 00:12:49,620
♪Spring breeze passes,
composing the fleeting years♪

249
00:12:50,540 --> 00:12:57,140
♪Clouds on Mount Wu,
no sails on the sea♪

250
00:12:57,300 --> 00:13:03,980
♪Wanting to fold
my heart into a paper kite♪

251
00:13:04,260 --> 00:13:10,700
♪But the ties are too tangled to sever♪

